{
  "video_id": "aupPrDnhrKA",
  "title": "How augmented reality could change the future of surgery | Nadine Hachach-Haram",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12857.0,
      "end_time": 15695.0,
      "text": "According to the theories of human social development,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15719.0,
      "end_time": 17936.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re now living through the fourth great epoch"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17960.0,
      "end_time": 20550.0,
      "text": "of technological advancement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20800.0,
      "end_time": 21279.0,
      "text": "the Information Age."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22240.0,
      "end_time": 25816.0,
      "text": "Connectivity through digital technology is a modern miracle."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25840.0,
      "end_time": 30976.0,
      "text": "We can say it has broken down barriers of time and space which separate people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31000.0,
      "end_time": 32896.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s created a condition for an age"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32920.0,
      "end_time": 35160.0,
      "text": "where information, ideas can be shared freely."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37240.0,
      "end_time": 40176.0,
      "text": "But are these great accomplishments in digital technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40200.0,
      "end_time": 42680.0,
      "text": "really the endgame in terms of what can be achieved?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43640.0,
      "end_time": 45560.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45800.0,
      "end_time": 46856.0,
      "text": "and today I&#39;d like to share with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46880.0,
      "end_time": 50160.0,
      "text": "how I believe digital technology can take us to even greater heights."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51880.0,
      "end_time": 53816.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a surgeon by profession,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53840.0,
      "end_time": 56216.0,
      "text": "and as I stand here today talking to all of you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56240.0,
      "end_time": 60616.0,
      "text": "five billion people around the world lack access to safe surgical care."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60640.0,
      "end_time": 63560.0,
      "text": "Five billion people."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63800.0,
      "end_time": 65696.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s 70 percent of the world&#39;s population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65720.0,
      "end_time": 68176.0,
      "text": "who according to the WHO&#39;s Lancet Commission"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68200.0,
      "end_time": 70976.0,
      "text": "can&#39;t even access simple surgical procedures"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71000.0,
      "end_time": 72320.0,
      "text": "as and when they need them."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73760.0,
      "end_time": 75816.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s zoom in on Sierra Leone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75840.0,
      "end_time": 78336.0,
      "text": "a country of six million people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78360.0,
      "end_time": 81840.0,
      "text": "where a recent study showed that there are only 10 qualified surgeons."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82520.0,
      "end_time": 85520.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s one surgeon for every 600,000 people."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86280.0,
      "end_time": 87800.0,
      "text": "The numbers are staggering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88680.0,
      "end_time": 90600.0,
      "text": "and we don&#39;t even need to look that far."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 91160.0,
      "end_time": 93295.0,
      "text": "If we look around us here in the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93320.0,
      "end_time": 98560.0,
      "text": "a recent study reported that we need an extra 100,000 surgeons by 2030"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98800.0,
      "end_time": 101480.0,
      "text": "to just keep up with the demand for routine surgical procedures."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102120.0,
      "end_time": 105240.0,
      "text": "At the rate that we&#39;re going, we won&#39;t be meeting those numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107520.0,
      "end_time": 110136.0,
      "text": "As a surgeon, this is a global issue that bothers me."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110160.0,
      "end_time": 111696.0,
      "text": "It bothers me a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111720.0,
      "end_time": 113536.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;ve seen firsthand"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113560.0,
      "end_time": 116416.0,
      "text": "how lack of access to safe and affordable healthcare"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116440.0,
      "end_time": 118360.0,
      "text": "can blight the lives of ordinary people."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 118960.0,
      "end_time": 121560.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re a patient that needs an operation"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121800.0,
      "end_time": 122816.0,
      "text": "and there isn&#39;t a surgeon available,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122840.0,
      "end_time": 125400.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re left with some really difficult choices:"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125840.0,
      "end_time": 128240.0,
      "text": "to wait, to travel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 129199.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130919.00000000001,
      "text": "or not to have an operation at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 132880.0,
      "end_time": 134120.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s the answer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 135000.0,
      "end_time": 139960.0,
      "text": "Well, part of you are carrying some of that solution with you today:"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 139120.0,
      "end_time": 141960.0,
      "text": "a smartphone, a tablet, a computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143800.0,
      "end_time": 144456.0,
      "text": "Because for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144480.0,
      "end_time": 148536.0,
      "text": "digital communications technology has the power to do so much more"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 148560.0,
      "end_time": 150816.0,
      "text": "than just to allow us to shop online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 150840.0,
      "end_time": 153888.0,
      "text": "to connect through social media platforms and to stay up to date."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 154880.0,
      "end_time": 159960.0,
      "text": "It has the power to help us solve some of the key issues that we face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 159120.0,
      "end_time": 161640.0,
      "text": "like lack of access to vital surgical services."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 162440.0,
      "end_time": 164176.0,
      "text": "And today I&#39;d like to share with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 164200.0,
      "end_time": 166640.0,
      "text": "an example of how I think we can make that possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 167360.0,
      "end_time": 169776.0,
      "text": "The history of surgery is filled with breakthroughs"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 169800.0,
      "end_time": 173136.0,
      "text": "in how science and technology was able to help the surgeons of the day"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 173160.0,
      "end_time": 174656.0,
      "text": "face their greatest challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 174680.0,
      "end_time": 176656.0,
      "text": "If we go back several hundred years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 176680.0,
      "end_time": 178576.0,
      "text": "an understanding of microbiology"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 178600.0,
      "end_time": 180936.0,
      "text": "led to the development of antiseptic techniques,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 180960.0,
      "end_time": 182816.0,
      "text": "which played a big role in making sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 182840.0,
      "end_time": 185176.0,
      "text": "patients were able to stay alive postsurgery."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 185200.0,
      "end_time": 186775.0,
      "text": "Fast-forward a few hundred years"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 186800.0,
      "end_time": 189136.0,
      "text": "and we developed keyhole or arthroscopic surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 189160.0,
      "end_time": 192550.0,
      "text": "which combines video technology and precision instruments"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 192800.0,
      "end_time": 193760.0,
      "text": "to make surgery less invasive."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 195760.0,
      "end_time": 199960.0,
      "text": "And more recently, a lot of you will be aware of robotic surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 199120.0,
      "end_time": 203776.0,
      "text": "and what robotics brings to surgery is much like modern automated machinery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 203800.0,
      "end_time": 205000.0,
      "text": "ultraprecision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 205680.0,
      "end_time": 209960.0,
      "text": "the ability to carry out procedures at the tiniest scales"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 209120.0,
      "end_time": 212400.0,
      "text": "with a degree of accuracy that even surpasses the human hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 214000.0,
      "end_time": 217640.0,
      "text": "But robotic surgery also introduced something else to surgery:"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 218480.0,
      "end_time": 219935.0,
      "text": "the idea that a surgeon"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 219960.0,
      "end_time": 223640.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t actually have to be standing at the patient&#39;s bedside to deliver care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 224320.0,
      "end_time": 226215.0,
      "text": "that he could be looking at a screen"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 226240.0,
      "end_time": 228400.0,
      "text": "and instructing a robot through a computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 229800.0,
      "end_time": 231880.0,
      "text": "We call this remote surgery."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 234800.0,
      "end_time": 236496.0,
      "text": "It is incumbent on us"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 236520.0,
      "end_time": 240976.0,
      "text": "to find solutions that solve these answers in a cost-effective and scalable way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 241000.0,
      "end_time": 243656.0,
      "text": "so that everyone, no matter where they are in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 243680.0,
      "end_time": 245320.0,
      "text": "can have these problems addressed."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 246440.0,
      "end_time": 248960.0,
      "text": "So what if I told you"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 248120.0,
      "end_time": 250496.0,
      "text": "that you didn&#39;t really need a million-dollar robot"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 250520.0,
      "end_time": 251760.0,
      "text": "to provide remote surgery?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 252720.0,
      "end_time": 256680.0,
      "text": "That all you needed was a phone, a tablet, or a computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 257680.0,
      "end_time": 259000.0,
      "text": "an internet connection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 259800.0,
      "end_time": 261616.0,
      "text": "a confident colleague on the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 261640.0,
      "end_time": 263200.0,
      "text": "and one magic ingredient:"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 264120.0,
      "end_time": 266880.0,
      "text": "an augmented reality collaboration software."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 268790.0,
      "end_time": 270815.0,
      "text": "Using this augmented reality collaboration software,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 270839.0,
      "end_time": 273896.0,
      "text": "an expert surgeon can now virtually transport himself"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 273920.0,
      "end_time": 275696.0,
      "text": "into any clinical setting"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 275720.0,
      "end_time": 278776.0,
      "text": "simply by using his phone or tablet or computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 278800.0,
      "end_time": 281656.0,
      "text": "and he can visually and practically interact in an operation"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 281680.0,
      "end_time": 283160.0,
      "text": "from start to finish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 283400.0,
      "end_time": 286640.0,
      "text": "guiding and mentoring a local doctor through the procedure step by step."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 287800.0,
      "end_time": 290160.0,
      "text": "Well, enough of me telling you about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 290400.0,
      "end_time": 291320.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d now like to show you."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 294840.0,
      "end_time": 297775.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re now going to go live to Dr. Marc Tompkins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 297800.0,
      "end_time": 300360.0,
      "text": "an orthopedic surgeon at the University of Minnesota."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 301800.0,
      "end_time": 304296.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s going to perform an arthroscopic surgery for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 304320.0,
      "end_time": 306496.0,
      "text": "a keyhole surgery of the knee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 306520.0,
      "end_time": 308560.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d like to disclose"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 308800.0,
      "end_time": 311240.0,
      "text": "that this patient has consented to having their operation streamed."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 314400.0,
      "end_time": 316696.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d also like to point out that in the interest of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 316720.0,
      "end_time": 318936.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re just going to go through the first steps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 318960.0,
      "end_time": 320215.0,
      "text": "marking up the patient"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 320240.0,
      "end_time": 323000.0,
      "text": "and just identifying a few key anatomical landmarks."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 324960.0,
      "end_time": 326919.0,
      "text": "Hello, Dr. Tompkins, can you hear me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 328200.0,
      "end_time": 330176.0,
      "text": "Dr. Mark Tompkins: Good morning, Nadine."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 330200.0,
      "end_time": 332616.0,
      "text": "Nadine Hachach-Haram: Everyone from TED says hello."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 332640.0,
      "end_time": 333840.0,
      "text": "Audience: Hi."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 336200.0,
      "end_time": 338496.0,
      "text": "NHH: Alright, Dr. Tompkins, let&#39;s get started."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 338520.0,
      "end_time": 341816.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s start with our incisions and where we&#39;re going to make these,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 341840.0,
      "end_time": 343775.0,
      "text": "on either side of the patellar tendon."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 343800.0,
      "end_time": 347496.0,
      "text": "So if you can make your incisions there and there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 347520.0,
      "end_time": 349640.0,
      "text": "that should hopefully get us into the knee."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 351000.0,
      "end_time": 352400.0,
      "text": "MT: All right, I&#39;m going in."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 353840.0,
      "end_time": 355390.0,
      "text": "NHH: Great."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 357480.0,
      "end_time": 359640.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re just getting inside the joint now."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 362520.0,
      "end_time": 365799.0,
      "text": "So why don&#39;t we go around and have a quick look at the meniscus."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 367680.0,
      "end_time": 368880.0,
      "text": "MT: Perfect."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 371960.0,
      "end_time": 375496.0,
      "text": "NHH: Great, so we can see there&#39;s a small tear there on the meniscus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 375520.0,
      "end_time": 377359.0,
      "text": "but otherwise it looks alright."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 378800.0,
      "end_time": 381216.0,
      "text": "And if you turn and head to this direction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 381240.0,
      "end_time": 382456.0,
      "text": "follow my finger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 382480.0,
      "end_time": 384680.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s have a quick look at the ACL and the PCL."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 386720.0,
      "end_time": 389936.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s your ACL there, that looks quite healthy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 389960.0,
      "end_time": 391215.0,
      "text": "no problems there."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 391240.0,
      "end_time": 394256.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve just identified that small meniscus tear there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 394280.0,
      "end_time": 397000.0,
      "text": "but otherwise the fluid around the joint looks OK as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 398920.0,
      "end_time": 402256.0,
      "text": "All right, thank you very much, Dr. Tompkins. Thank you for your time."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 402280.0,
      "end_time": 403895.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll let you continue."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 403920.0,
      "end_time": 406256.0,
      "text": "Have a good day. Bye."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 406280.0,
      "end_time": 408359.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 414840.0,
      "end_time": 416895.0,
      "text": "So I hope through this simple demonstration"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 416920.0,
      "end_time": 420816.0,
      "text": "I was able to illustrate to you just how powerful this technology can be."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 420840.0,
      "end_time": 424560.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d like to point out that I wasn&#39;t using any special equipment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 424800.0,
      "end_time": 426536.0,
      "text": "just my laptop and a really simple webcam."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 426560.0,
      "end_time": 428536.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re so used to using digital technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 428560.0,
      "end_time": 430800.0,
      "text": "to communicate through voice and text and video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 431760.0,
      "end_time": 435560.0,
      "text": "but augmented reality can do something so much deeper."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 435800.0,
      "end_time": 437376.0,
      "text": "It allows two people to virtually interact"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 437400.0,
      "end_time": 440114.0,
      "text": "in a way that mimics how they would collaborate in person."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 441200.0,
      "end_time": 443416.0,
      "text": "Being able to show someone what you want to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 443440.0,
      "end_time": 445576.0,
      "text": "to illustrate and demonstrate and gesture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 445600.0,
      "end_time": 447840.0,
      "text": "is so much more powerful than just telling them."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 448840.0,
      "end_time": 451560.0,
      "text": "And it can make for such a great learning tool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 451800.0,
      "end_time": 453440.0,
      "text": "because we learn better through direct experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 454400.0,
      "end_time": 456496.0,
      "text": "So how is this making a difference around the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 456520.0,
      "end_time": 458575.0,
      "text": "Well, back in my teaching hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 458600.0,
      "end_time": 461696.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve been using this to support local district general hospitals"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 461720.0,
      "end_time": 464320.0,
      "text": "and providing skin cancer surgery and trauma treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 464800.0,
      "end_time": 468176.0,
      "text": "Now, patients can access care at a local level."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 468200.0,
      "end_time": 471536.0,
      "text": "This reduces their travel time, improves their access,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 471560.0,
      "end_time": 472760.0,
      "text": "and saves money."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 473680.0,
      "end_time": 476976.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve even started seeing its use in wound care management with nurses"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 477000.0,
      "end_time": 478736.0,
      "text": "and in outpatient management."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 478760.0,
      "end_time": 480496.0,
      "text": "Most recently, and quite exciting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 480520.0,
      "end_time": 484560.0,
      "text": "it was used in supporting a surgeon through a cancer removal of a kidney."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 486320.0,
      "end_time": 489159.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d like to just share with you a very quick video here."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 489760.0,
      "end_time": 492320.0,
      "text": "I apologize for some of the gruesome views."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 494800.0,
      "end_time": 497320.0,
      "text": "(Video) Doctor 1: OK. Show me again."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 497760.0,
      "end_time": 499856.0,
      "text": "Doctor 2: If you see here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 499880.0,
      "end_time": 503936.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the upper part, the most outer part of your tumor."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 503960.0,
      "end_time": 505215.0,
      "text": "Doctor 1: Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 505240.0,
      "end_time": 508960.0,
      "text": "Doctor 2: So it&#39;s three centimeters deep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 508120.0,
      "end_time": 510000.0,
      "text": "so this should be three centimeters."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 510840.0,
      "end_time": 512175.0,
      "text": "Doctor 1: Yes, yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 512200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516800.00000000006,
      "text": "Doctor 2: OK, so you need to get a 3.5 margin."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 517534.99999999994,
      "end_time": 519534.99999999994,
      "text": "Doctor 1: I&#39;m going to show you anyway"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 519558.99999999994,
      "end_time": 522118.99999999994,
      "text": "and tell me what you think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 522880.0,
      "end_time": 526256.0,
      "text": "NHH: We&#39;re also seeing the use of this technology at a global scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 526280.0,
      "end_time": 528815.0,
      "text": "and one of the most heartwarming stories I can recall"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 528840.0,
      "end_time": 532800.0,
      "text": "is from the town of Trujillo in the north of Lima in Peru,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 532840.0,
      "end_time": 535696.0,
      "text": "where this technology was used to support the provision"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 535720.0,
      "end_time": 538336.0,
      "text": "of cleft lip and palate surgery to children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 538360.0,
      "end_time": 542336.0,
      "text": "children from poor backgrounds who didn&#39;t have access to health insurance."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 542360.0,
      "end_time": 544976.0,
      "text": "And in this town, there was a hospital with one surgeon"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 545000.0,
      "end_time": 546936.0,
      "text": "working hard to provide this care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 546960.0,
      "end_time": 548160.0,
      "text": "Dr. Soraya."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 548960.0,
      "end_time": 551456.0,
      "text": "Now, Dr. Soraya was struggling under the sheer demand"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 551480.0,
      "end_time": 552896.0,
      "text": "of her local population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 552920.0,
      "end_time": 556496.0,
      "text": "as well as the fact that she wasn&#39;t specifically trained in this procedure."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 556520.0,
      "end_time": 558216.0,
      "text": "And so, with the help of a charity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 558240.0,
      "end_time": 561696.0,
      "text": "we were able to connect her with a cleft surgeon in California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 561720.0,
      "end_time": 565160.0,
      "text": "and using this technology, he was able to guide her and her colleagues"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 565400.0,
      "end_time": 566736.0,
      "text": "through the procedure step by step,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 566760.0,
      "end_time": 568936.0,
      "text": "guiding them, training them and teaching them."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 568960.0,
      "end_time": 570216.0,
      "text": "Within a few months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 570240.0,
      "end_time": 572696.0,
      "text": "they were able to perform 30 percent more operations"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 572720.0,
      "end_time": 574816.0,
      "text": "with less and less complications."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 574840.0,
      "end_time": 578256.0,
      "text": "And now Dr. Soraya and her team can perform these operations"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 578280.0,
      "end_time": 581160.0,
      "text": "independently, competently and confidently."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 582000.0,
      "end_time": 584776.0,
      "text": "And I remember one quote from a mother who said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 584800.0,
      "end_time": 586920.0,
      "text": "\"This technology gave my daughter her smile.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 588640.0,
      "end_time": 591800.0,
      "text": "For me, this is the real power of this technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 591800.0,
      "end_time": 594175.0,
      "text": "The beauty is that it breaks boundaries."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 594200.0,
      "end_time": 597560.0,
      "text": "It transcends all technological difficulties."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 598520.0,
      "end_time": 601000.0,
      "text": "It connects people. It democratizes access."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 602160.0,
      "end_time": 604415.0,
      "text": "Wi-Fi and mobile technology are growing rapidly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 604440.0,
      "end_time": 607456.0,
      "text": "and they should play a role in boosting surgical provision."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 607480.0,
      "end_time": 610936.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve even seen it used in conflict zones where there&#39;s considerable risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 610960.0,
      "end_time": 613496.0,
      "text": "in getting specialist surgeons to certain locations."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 613520.0,
      "end_time": 616415.0,
      "text": "In a world where there are more mobile devices"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 616440.0,
      "end_time": 618296.0,
      "text": "than there are human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 618320.0,
      "end_time": 620200.0,
      "text": "it truly has a global reach."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 620920.0,
      "end_time": 622736.0,
      "text": "Of course, we&#39;ve still got a long way"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 622760.0,
      "end_time": 626256.0,
      "text": "before we can solve the problem of getting surgery to five billion people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 626280.0,
      "end_time": 627536.0,
      "text": "and unfortunately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 627560.0,
      "end_time": 629800.0,
      "text": "some people still don&#39;t have access to internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 630520.0,
      "end_time": 633790.0,
      "text": "But things are rapidly moving in the right direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 634360.0,
      "end_time": 636800.0,
      "text": "The potential for change is there."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 636840.0,
      "end_time": 639776.0,
      "text": "My team and I are growing our global footprint,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 639800.0,
      "end_time": 642719.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re starting to see the potential of this technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 644440.0,
      "end_time": 646336.0,
      "text": "Through digital technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 646360.0,
      "end_time": 649656.0,
      "text": "through simple, everyday devices that we take for granted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 649680.0,
      "end_time": 651695.0,
      "text": "through devices of the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 651720.0,
      "end_time": 653680.0,
      "text": "we can really do miraculous things."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 654360.0,
      "end_time": 655576.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 655600.0,
      "end_time": 658840.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}